quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Ibarura ry’abantu riregereje, mu gihe bo bari mu burangare, birengagije (amategeko ya Allah)"
  21,2,Nta rwibutso rushya rubageraho ruturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo ngo barwumve batarukerensa
  21,3,"Imitima yabo ihugiye (mu bibi). Naho inkozi z’ibibi zongorerana zigira ziti \"Ese uyu (Muhamadi) hari ikindi ari cyo usibye kuba ari umuntu nkamwe? Ese muremera gukurikira uburozi kandi mububona"
  21,4,"(Muhamadi) aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye azi ibivugwa mu kirere no ku isi (byose), kandi ni Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  21,5,"Ahubwo baravuze bati \"(Iyi Qur’an) ni inzozi z’uruvangitirane, (abandi bati) ahubwo yarayihimbye! (Abandi bati) ahubwo ni umusizi! Ngaho natuzanire igitangaza nk’uko (intumwa) zo hambere zoherejwe (zibifite)"
  21,6,Nta mudugudu n’umwe mu yo tworetse mbere yabo wigeze wemera (ari uko ubonye ibitangaza); ese ni bo bakwemera
  21,7,"Kandi nta ntumwa twigeze twohereza mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi) batari abagabo, tuzihishuriye ubutumwa. Ngaho nimubaze abahawe ubumenyi (bw’ibitabo byo hambere) niba mutabizi"
  21,8,"Kandi (intumwa)ntitwazihaye imibiri idakenera ibyo kurya, ndetse ntizanabayeho ubuziraherezo"
  21,9,"Hanyuma twazuzurije isezerano, nuko tuzirokorana n’abo twashakaga, maze tworeka abanyabyaha"
  21,10,Rwose twabahishuriye igitabo (Qur’an) gikubiyemo urwibutso rwanyu. Ese nta bwenge mugira
  21,11,"Ni imidugudu ingahe yakoraga ibikorwa bibi twarimbuye, maze nyuma yayo tukazana abandi bantu"
  21,12,"Nuko babonye ibihano byacu, (bagerageza) kwirukababihunga"
  21,13,"(Babwirwa bannyegwa bati) \"Mwihunga! Ahubwo nimusubire mu buzima bw’umunezerono mu ngo zanyu, kugira ngo mukomeze musabwe (nk’uko byari bisanzwe)"
  21,14,"Baravuga bati \"Mbega ibyago byacu! Mu by’ukuri, twari inkozi z’ibibi"
  21,15,"Ayo ni yo yakomeje kuba amaganya yabo, kugeza ubwo tubagize nk’imyaka yarandaguwe, ikazima"
  21,16,Ntabwo twaremye ikirere n’isi n’ibiri hagatiyabyo dukina
  21,17,"Iyo tuza kuba dushaka ibitunezeza (kugira umwana cyangwa umugore), twari kubyitoranyiriza iwacu (mu ijuru) iyo koko tuza kuba turi ababikora"
  21,18,"Ahubwo tugaragaza ukuri kugasenya ikinyoma, maze kikayoyoka. Kandi muzahanishwa ibihanobikaze kubera ibyo mwitirira Allah (muvuga ko afite umugore n’umwana)"
  21,19,Ibiri mu birere no ku isi ni ibye. Kandi abari iwe (abamalayika) ntibagira ubwibone bwo kumusenga ndetsentibananirwa
  21,20,"Basingiza (Allah) ijoro n’amanywa, (kandi) ntibarambirwa"
  21,21,Ese ni gute (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriyeho ibigirwamana bidashobora kuzura (abapfuye) bibakuye mu butaka
  21,22,"Iyo (mu kirere no ku isi) haza kuba hari izindi mana zitari Allah, byombi byari guhungabana. Ubutungane ni ubwa Allah, Nyagasani nyir’intebe y’icyubahiro, ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  21,23,"(Allah) ntabazwaibyo akora, nyamara bo (ibiremwa) bazabazwa (ibyo bakora)"
  21,24,"Ese (ababangikanyamana) bishyiriyeho izindi mana zitari we? Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ngaho nimuzane ikimenyetso cyanyu (gihamya ukuri kw’ibyo musenga). Iyi (Qur’an) ni urwibutso ku bari kumwe nanjye (abemera), ikaba n’urwibutso ku babayeho mbere yanjye(kuko ibitabo byayibanjirije nabyo byahakanye ko Imana ibangikanywa). Ariko abenshi muri bo ntibazi ukuri, ahubwo barakwirengagiza"
  21,25,Kandi nta ntumwa twigeze twohereza mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi) ngo tubure kuyihishurira ko nta yindi mana ibaho ikwiriye gusengwa mu kuri itari njye (Allah).Bityo nimungaragire (njyenyine)
  21,26,"Kandi (Ababangikanyamana) baravuze bati \"(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe afite umwana. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe (ntibibaho ko yagira umwana)! Ahubwo (abo bamalayika bita abana be) ni abagaragu bubashywe"
  21,27,"Ntacyo bajya bavuga batagitegetswe (na Allah), kandi bubahiriza itegeko rye"
  21,28,"(Abo bamalayika, Allah) azi ibibabaho n’ibizababaho, kandi ntibashobora kugira uwo bavuganira (Allah) atamwishimiye. Ndetse bahora bicishije bugufi kubera kumutinya"